---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="fr"
  title="Inscription — Hamilton"
  description="Formulaire d'inscription pour le centre Le Ballon Rouge de Hamilton. Demandez une place pour votre enfant."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-10 pt-8 md:pt-12">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-red-50 px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-red-700 ring-1 ring-red-100">
      Hamilton
    </div>
    <h1 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-5xl">Inscription — Hamilton</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 max-w-prose text-base font-medium leading-7 text-slate-600 md:text-lg">
      Remplissez le formulaire ci-dessous pour inscrire votre enfant sur la liste d'attente du centre de Hamilton. Votre demande sera transmise directement à notre superviseure à
      <a href="mailto:inscription@ballonrouge.ca" class="font-extrabold text-red-700 underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-red-900">inscription@ballonrouge.ca</a>.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a
        href="/inscription/"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/80 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:bg-white"
      >
        ← Retour à l'inscription
      </a>
      <a
        href="/inscription/brantford/"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-black/10 bg-white/80 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-800 shadow-sm hover:bg-white"
      >
        Voir Brantford
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main content -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-16">
    <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-5">

      <!-- Left: info -->
      <aside class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-4">

        <article class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-xl shadow-black/5">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-black tracking-tight">Coordonnées</h2>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span>📍</span> 135 Bendamere Ave, Hamilton, ON L9C 1N4</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span>🕐</span> Lun–Ven 7h00–17h30</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span>👶</span> Bambins &amp; préscolaires</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span>🇫🇷</span> Français au quotidien</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="mt-4 space-y-2">
            <a href="tel:9053838371" class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white/60 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-800 hover:bg-white">
              📞 905-383-8371
            </a>
            <a href="mailto:leballonrouge@cscmonavenir.ca" class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-black/10 bg-white/60 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-red-700 hover:bg-white">
              ✉️ leballonrouge@cscmonavenir.ca
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-[28px] border border-amber-100 bg-amber-50/60 p-5 shadow-lg shadow-black/5">
          <p class="text-sm font-extrabold text-amber-800">⏱️ Règle des 48 heures</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-amber-700">
            Lorsqu'une place se libère, vous avez <strong>48 heures</strong> pour confirmer. Sans réponse dans ce délai, la place sera offerte à la famille suivante sur la liste.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-[28px] border border-black/10 bg-white/70 p-5 shadow-lg shadow-black/5">
          <p class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-900">📋 Priorités d'admission</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-slate-600">
            La priorité est accordée aux familles francophones, aux frères et sœurs d'enfants inscrits, et aux enfants du personnel. Consultez la
            <a href="/inscription/#conditions" class="font-extrabold text-red-700 underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-red-900">page d'inscription</a>
            pour la liste complète.
          </p>
        </article>

      </aside>

      <!-- Right: form -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3">
        <article class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[28px] border border-red-700/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-2xl shadow-red-700/10 ring-1 ring-black/5 md:p-10">
          <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -inset-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 via-white to-orange-50 opacity-70 blur-2xl"></div>

          <div class="relative">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-2xl">Formulaire d'inscription</h2>
            <p class="mt-1 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500">
              Tous les champs marqués <span class="text-red-600">*</span> sont obligatoires.
            </p>

            <form
              class="mt-6 space-y-10"
              action={`mailto:inscription@ballonrouge.ca`}
              method="POST"
              enctype="multipart/form-data"
              onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('Merci! Votre demande a été soumise. (démo)');"
            >

              <!-- Information Enfant -->
              <section class="space-y-5">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-black/10"></div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900">👶 Information Enfant</h3>
                  <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-black/10"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
                  <label class="space-y-1">
                    <span class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Nom <span class="text-red-600">*</span></span>
                    <input name="enfant_nom" required class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 font-semibold shadow-sm outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/40" />
                  </label>
                  <label class="space-y-1">
                    <span class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Prénom <span class="text-red-600">*</span></span>
                    <input name="enfant_prenom" required class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 font-semibold shadow-sm outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/40" />
                  </label>
                  <label class="space-y-1">
                    <span class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Date de naissance <span class="text-red-600">*</span></span>
                    <input name="enfant_ddn" required type="date" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 font-semibold shadow-sm outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/40" />
                  </label>
                  <label class="space-y-1">
                    <span class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Genre <span class="text-red-600">*</span></span>
                    <select name="enfant_genre" required class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 font-semibold shadow-sm outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/40">
                      <option value="">Choisir…</option>
                      <option>Féminin</option>
                      <option>Masculin</option>
                      <option>Autre</option>
                      <option>Préfère ne pas répondre</option>
                    </select>
                  </label>
                  <label class="space-y-1">
                    <span class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Date de début souhaitée <span class="text-red-600">*</span></span>
                    <input name="enfant_debut" required type="date" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 font-semibold shadow-sm outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/40" />
                  </label>
                </div>

                <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
                  <fieldset class="space-y-2">
                    <legend class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Langue <span class="text-red-600">*</span></legend>
                    <label class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-slate-800">
                      <input required type="radio" name="enfant_langue" value="Français" /> Français
                    </label>
                    <label class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-slate-800">
                      <input type="radio" name="enfant_langue" value="Anglais" /> Anglais
                    </label>
                  </fieldset>

                  <fieldset class="space-y-2">
                    <legend class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Groupe <span class="text-red-600">*</span></legend>
                    <label class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-slate-800">
                      <input required type="radio" name="enfant_groupe" value="Bambins" /> Bambins
                    </label>
                    <label class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-slate-800">
                      <input type="radio" name="enfant_groupe" value="Préscolaire" /> Préscolaire
                    </label>
                  </fieldset>

                  <fieldset class="space-y-2">
                    <legend class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Subvention <span class="text-red-600">*</span></legend>
                    <label class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-slate-800">
                      <input required type="radio" name="enfant_subvention" value="Oui" /> Oui
                    </label>
                    <label class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-slate-800">
                      <input type="radio" name="enfant_subvention" value="Non" /> Non
                    </label>
                  </fieldset>
                </div>

                <fieldset class="space-y-2">
                  <legend class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Programme <span class="text-red-600">*</span></legend>
                  <label class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-slate-800">
                    <input required type="radio" name="enfant_programme" value="Temps partiel" /> Temps partiel
                  </label>
                  <label class="flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold text-slate-800">
                    <input type="radio" name="enfant_programme" value="Temps plein" /> Temps plein (Jours)
                  </label>
                </fieldset>

                <label class="space-y-1">
                  <span class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Commentaire</span>
                  <textarea name="enfant_commentaire" rows="3" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 font-semibold shadow-sm outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/40" placeholder="Informations supplémentaires, besoins particuliers, etc."></textarea>
                </label>
              </section>

              <hr class="border-slate-200" />

              <!-- Information Parent -->
              <section class="space-y-5">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-black/10"></div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900">👨‍👩‍👧 Information Parent</h3>
                  <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-black/10"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
                  <label class="space-y-1">
                    <span class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Nom <span class="text-red-600">*</span></span>
                    <input name="parent_nom" required class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 font-semibold shadow-sm outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/40" />
                  </label>
                  <label class="space-y-1">
                    <span class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Prénom <span class="text-red-600">*</span></span>
                    <input name="parent_prenom" required class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 font-semibold shadow-sm outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/40" />
                  </label>
                  <label class="space-y-1">
                    <span class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Téléphone <span class="text-red-600">*</span></span>
                    <input name="parent_tel" required inputmode="tel" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 font-semibold shadow-sm outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/40" />
                  </label>
                  <label class="space-y-1">
                    <span class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Courriel <span class="text-red-600">*</span></span>
                    <input name="parent_email" required type="email" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 font-semibold shadow-sm outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/40" />
                  </label>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 pt-2">
                  <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-black/10"></div>
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Adresse</h4>
                  <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-black/10"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
                  <label class="space-y-1 sm:col-span-2">
                    <span class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Rue <span class="text-red-600">*</span></span>
                    <input name="adresse_rue" required class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 font-semibold shadow-sm outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/40" />
                  </label>
                  <label class="space-y-1">
                    <span class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Ville <span class="text-red-600">*</span></span>
                    <input name="adresse_ville" required class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 font-semibold shadow-sm outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/40" />
                  </label>
                  <label class="space-y-1">
                    <span class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Province <span class="text-red-600">*</span></span>
                    <input name="adresse_province" required value="Ontario" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 font-semibold shadow-sm outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/40" />
                  </label>
                  <label class="space-y-1">
                    <span class="text-sm font-extrabold text-slate-700">Code postal <span class="text-red-600">*</span></span>
                    <input name="adresse_cp" required class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-3 font-semibold shadow-sm outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/40" placeholder="ex: L9C 1N4" />
                  </label>
                </div>
              </section>

              <button
                type="submit"
                class="w-full rounded-2xl bg-red-700 px-6 py-4 text-sm font-extrabold text-white shadow-lg shadow-red-700/20 hover:bg-red-800"
              >
                Envoyer la demande d'inscription →
              </button>

              <p class="text-center text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400">
                Votre demande sera transmise à
                <a href="mailto:inscription@ballonrouge.ca" class="text-red-700 underline underline-offset-4">inscription@ballonrouge.ca</a>.
                La superviseure vous contactera pour confirmer la réception.
              </p>

            </form>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>